name: Rainbows & Wishes
description:
This is an awesome hand cast resin charm/pendant that comes on an 18 inch silver plated chain

This resin charm is possibly my favourite not that i am meant to have favourites but this one just is so bright and colourful like all the colours of the rainbow packed into a small bead packed into clear resin its so bold and embodies what rocktastic plastic is all about
bright bold and beautiful

The charm measurements are as follows

Width 1/2 Inch
Length 1.1/2 Inches (one and a half inches)

Custom ?- Fancy this pendant but in a different colour-Just message me and i will see what i can do for you

name: Elegance
description:
This is an awesome hand cast resin charm/pendant that comes on an 18 inch silver plated chain
